@startuml
title Athena SDK Cookie Helpers (After)

skinparam backgroundColor White
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor Black
skinparam DefaultTextColor Black
skinparam Rectangle {
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}

rectangle "Consumer App\n(Next.js middleware / proxy)" as consumer #F3F7FF
rectangle "@xylex-group/athena/cookies\n(new SDK subpath)" as cookies #E9FCEB
rectangle "@xylex-group/athena\n(auth + gateway client)" as sdk #F8F8F8
rectangle "Athena Auth Server\n(Rust athena-auth runtime)" as server #FFF7E8

consumer --> cookies : getSessionCookie(request)\ngetCookieCache(request, secret)\nsetRequestCookie(...)
consumer --> sdk : auth/gateway calls
consumer --> server : request with validated cookie/header handling
cookies --> consumer : consistent prefix handling\n(athena-auth + legacy fallback)
sdk --> server : auth API calls

note bottom of cookies
SDK-only helper module:
- better-auth-like getSessionCookie signature
- cookie parsing / Set-Cookie merge utils
- compact/jwt cookie-cache verification helpers
No server-runtime dependency added to athena-js.
end note
@enduml
